- Oakeshottian practice theory: 4 papers - Political knowledge is practical
  "knowing how" embedded in inherited practices
- Hayekian spontaneous order: 5 papers - Traditions encode dispersed tacit
  knowledge solving coordination problems
- Contemporary conservative synthesis: 3 papers - Balancing tradition's value
  with reform necessity
